{"tid":1371780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黑社會頭子689] 梁振英稱向警隊致敬　與警隊爲敵的暴徒是不自量力","createTime":"2019-07-27T10:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T10:15:03.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0e8bf2f54a0f9d2fa62e048a433cc89ea5e0d645","tid":1371780,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T10:09:21.000Z","msg":"全國政協副主席、前特首梁振英今（27日）則在facebook賬戶上發貼文，稱向優秀的香港警隊致敬。他指香港警隊有堅强實力及龐大資源，任何狂徒暴徒與警隊爲敵，皆不自量力，且會被繩之於法，<span style=\"color: red;\">更指被捕人士入獄前都會「夾著尾巴」向法庭求情。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3088021/org/d182b406b75f2689103a5eed50e757a9.JPG/MU4LSUBSG-tvxj_aYaErOt2ZdfAzdvlF8N4FfPDeBXw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3088021%2Forg%2Fd182b406b75f2689103a5eed50e757a9.JPG%2FMU4LSUBSG-tvxj_aYaErOt2ZdfAzdvlF8N4FfPDeBXw&h=67e49872&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b6ffc1464e8be6f934f467140fd689f6cd9884e","tid":1371780,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T10:12:03.000Z","msg":"夾著尾巴向法庭求情<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170214/s00001/1487065691733SL4_00980D1D301754A96EBCE099DC5B4A5B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170214%2Fs00001%2F1487065691733SL4_00980D1D301754A96EBCE099DC5B4A5B.jpg&h=4effa279&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20f2ad18c8a103642376855a8af5780fcd12db8f","tid":1371780,"uid":30782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e8bf2f54a0f9d2fa62e048a433cc89ea5e0d645","tid":1371780,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T10:09:21.000Z","msg":"全國政協副主席、前特首梁振英今（27日）則在facebook賬戶上發貼文，稱向優秀的香港警隊致敬。他指香港警隊有堅强實力及龐大資源，任何狂徒暴徒與警隊爲敵，皆不自量力，且會被繩之於法，<span style=\"color: red;\">更指被捕人士入獄前都會「夾著尾巴」向法庭求情。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3088021/org/d182b406b75f2689103a5eed50e757a9.JPG/MU4LSUBSG-tvxj_aYaErOt2ZdfAzdvlF8N4FfPDeBXw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3088021%2Forg%2Fd182b406b75f2689103a5eed50e757a9.JPG%2FMU4LSUBSG-tvxj_aYaErOt2ZdfAzdvlF8N4FfPDeBXw&h=67e49872&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T10:13:14.000Z","msg":"呢條死廢老"},{"pid":"2c434d724a1a734455ae594d9b6feb6a9c0d7e24","tid":1371780,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T10:15:03.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"}]}